# ==============================================================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# ==============================================================================
#
# ✅ DO:
# - Use VITE_ prefix for variables exposed to the browser (Vite apps)
# - Use NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix for variables exposed to the browser (Next.js apps)
# - Keep SERVICE_ROLE_KEY and SECRET_KEY server-side only
# - Use different keys for development, staging, and production
# - Rotate API keys regularly
#
# ❌ DON'T:
# - Commit .env.local or .env files to Git
# - Expose service role keys to the browser
# - Use production keys in development
# - Share API keys in screenshots or documentation
# - Hard-code keys in source code
#
